      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DREAM DESIGN (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.51) from Box 2 at this track. Has a strong record from this draw, notching three wins and two minor placings from five starts. Can find winning form. WILMA FLINTSTONE (5) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths second (24.13) over 407m at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. AKELA KUNG FU (7) had been racing well with a Mix 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Q Lakeside. Expected to do much better this time. KERRI BEACH (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
